Description:
    Creates a model broken down into many small files

Example:
    rails generate concerns Thing

    This will create:
      app/models/thing.rb
      app/models/thing
      app/models/thing/thing_active_record.rb
      app/models/thing/thing_class_methods.rb
      app/models/thing/thing_extensions.rb
      app/models/thing/thing_instance_methods.rb
      app/models/thing/thing_search.rb
      app/models/thing/thing_scopes.rb
      db/migrate/....create_things.rb
      spec/factories/things.rb
      spec/models/thing
      spec/models/thing/thing_active_record_spec.rb
      spec/models/thing/thing_class_methods_spec.rb
      spec/models/thing/thing_extensions_spec.rb
      spec/models/thing/thing_instance_methods_spec.rb
      spec/models/thing/thing_search_spec.rb
      spec/models/thing/thing_scopes_spec.rb
